22:18:05.000Z","msg":"可否講多两句<br />\n分享吓觀點？"},{"pid":"2fc71d0a6e45591f351af27c5ccfaa1b50b55045","tid":2509281,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d9e79465468ce69635461166f0d6619048d6b7","tid":2509281,"uid":318720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf641ade0bc4023093d511bbac3b0ede47cbb4b1","tid":2509281,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T22:10:04.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n唐錢兩人直頭係戰犯來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T22:18:05.000Z","msg":"可否講多两句<br />\n分享吓觀點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T22:20:55.000Z","msg":"咁覺得係咩宣傳大中華膠之類<br />\n一個地方出事﹐就屌反共既文人﹐都唔屌奶共班契弟<br />\n點解?因為讀書少﹐淨係識果一兩個人﹐咪拎出黎點相囉。<br />\n講到底﹐只係文化捉鬼而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}